span> 標題：監獄、監牢、地牢（prison, dungeon）</h1><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">經文出處</h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-sets\">\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Hebrew</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">來： בַּיִת, אסר, אָסִיר, אֵסוּר</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音譯： beyth ’esur, beyth ’asurim, beyth hasurim)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg16:21\">JDG 16:21</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg16:21\">JDG 16:21</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg16:21\">JDG 16:21</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg16:25\">JDG 16:25</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg16:25\">JDG 16:25</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl4:14\">ECC 4:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer37:15\">JER 37:15</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Hebrew</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">來： בַּיִת, בּוֹר</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音譯： (beyth) bor)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen40:15\">GEN 40:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen41:14\">GEN 41:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod12:29\">EXO 12:29</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa24:22\">ISA 24:22</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer37:16\">JER 37:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer38:6\">JER 38:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer38:7\">JER 38:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer38:9\">JER 38:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer38:10\">JER 38:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer38:11\">JER 38:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer38:13\">JER 38:13</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Hebrew</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">來： בַּיִת, כֶּלֶא, כְּלִיא</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音譯： (beyth) kele’, beyth kelu’)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs22:27\">1KI 22:27</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs17:4\">2KI 17:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs25:27\">2KI 25:27</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs25:29\">2KI 25:29</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr18:26\">2CH 18:26</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa42:7\">ISA 42:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa42:22\">ISA 42:22</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer37:4\">JER 37:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer37:15\">JER 37:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer37:18\">JER 37:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer52:31\">JER 52:31</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer52:33\">JER 52:33</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Hebrew</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">來： בַּיִת, מִשְׁמָר</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音譯： beyth mishmar)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen42:19\">GEN 42:19</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Hebrew</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">來： בַּיִת, פְּקֻדָּה</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音譯： beyth pqudoth)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer52:11\">JER 52:11</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Hebrew</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">來： בַּיִת, סֹהַר</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音譯： beyth sohar)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen39:20\">GEN 39:20</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen39:20\">GEN 39:20</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen39:21\">GEN 39:21</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen39:22\">GEN 39:22</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen39:22\">GEN 39:22</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen39:23\">GEN 39:23</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen40:3\">GEN 40:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen40:3\">GEN 40:3</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Aramaic</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">蘭：גֹּב</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音譯： gov)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan6:8\">DAN 6:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan6:13\">DAN 6:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan6:17\">DAN 6:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan6:18\">DAN 6:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan6:20\">DAN 6:20</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan6:21\">DAN 6:21</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan6:24\">DAN 6:24</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan6:24\">DAN 6:24</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan6:25\">DAN 6:25</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan6:25\">DAN 6:25</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Hebrew</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">來： מַטָּרָה</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音譯： matarah)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh3:25\">NEH 3:25</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh12:39\">NEH 12:39</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer32:2\">JER 32:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer32:8\">JER 32:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer32:12\">JER 32:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer33:1\">JER 33:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer37:21\">JER 37:21</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer37:21\">JER 37:21</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer38:6\">JER 38:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer38:13\">JER 38:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer38:28\">JER 38:28</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer39:14\">JER 39:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer39:15\">JER 39:15</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Hebrew</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">來： מַסְגֵּר</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音譯： masger)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps142:8\">PSA 142:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa24:22\">ISA 24:22</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa42:7\">ISA 42:7</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Hebrew</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">來： עֹצֶר</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音譯： ‘otser)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa53:8\">ISA 53:8</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Greek</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">希： δεσμωτήριον</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音譯： desmōtērion)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt11:2\">MAT 11:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts5:21\">ACT 5:21</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts5:23\">ACT 5:23</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts16:26\">ACT 16:26</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Greek</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">希： εἱρκτή</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音譯： heirktē)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Wis17:15\">WIS 17:15</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Greek</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">希： λάκκος</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音譯： lakkos)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Wis10:14\">WIS 10:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Bel1:31\">BEL 1:31</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Bel1:32\">BEL 1:32</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Bel1:34\">BEL 1:34</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Bel1:35\">BEL 1:35</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Bel1:36\">BEL 1:36</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Bel1:40\">BEL 1:40</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Bel1:42\">BEL 1:42</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/4Macc18:13\">4MA 18:13</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Greek</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">希： τήρησις</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音譯： tērēsis)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts4:3\">ACT 4:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts5:18\">ACT 5:18</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Greek</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">希： φυλακή</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音譯： fulakē)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt5:25\">MAT 5:25</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt14:3\">MAT 14:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt14:10\">MAT 14:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt18:30\">MAT 18:30</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt25:36\">MAT 25:36</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt25:39\">MAT 25:39</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt25:43\">MAT 25:43</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt25:44\">MAT 25:44</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark6:17\">MRK 6:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark6:27\">MRK 6:27</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke3:20\">LUK 3:20</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke12:58\">LUK 12:58</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke21:12\">LUK 21:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke22:33\">LUK 22:33</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke23:19\">LUK 23:19</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke23:25\">LUK 23:25</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John3:24\">JHN 3:24</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts5:19\">ACT 5:19</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts5:22\">ACT 5:22</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts5:25\">ACT 5:25</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts8:3\">ACT 8:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts12:4\">ACT 12:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts12:5\">ACT 12:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts12:6\">ACT 12:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts12:17\">ACT 12:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts16:23\">ACT 16:23</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts16:24\">ACT 16:24</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts16:27\">ACT 16:27</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts16:37\">ACT 16:37</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts16:40\">ACT 16:40</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts22:4\">ACT 22:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts26:10\">ACT 26:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor6:5\">2CO 6:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor11:23\">2CO 11:23</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb11:36\">HEB 11:36</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet3:19\">1PE 3:19</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev2:10\">REV 2:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev20:7\">REV 20:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/4Macc18:11\">4MA 18:11</a></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">描述和用途</h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-paragraphs\">\n<p>\n            <figure class=\"thlex-image\"><img class=\"thlex-img\" src=\"images/OAI-0043_paul_silas.png\" alt=\"OAI-0043_paul_silas\"><figcaption class=\"thlex-caption\"> (Image generated by ChatGPT using OpenAI technology)</figcaption></figure>監獄是關押罪犯或其他囚犯的地方。監獄或監牢沒有標準的大小或建築結構。</p>\n<hr/>\n</div>\n</div><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">翻譯</h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-paragraphs\">\n<p>幾乎所有語言都有表示監獄或監牢的詞語，但在某些情況下，可能要使用描述性短語，例如「把人綁起來的地方」或「人被鏈子鎖起來的地方」。在有些語言中，人們會使用一些慣用語，例如「吃鐵的地方」或「與老鼠呆在一起的房間」。譯文要傳遞出這樣的意思：這是一個違背某人的意志、強行約束他的地方。</p>\n<p>希伯來文<em>bor</em> 、亞蘭文<em>gov</em> 和希臘文<em>lakkos</em> 都是指地上的洞或凹坑。在<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer38:0\">JER 38:0</a> 中，耶利米被下到<em>bor</em> ，這可能是一個蓄水池（參<a class=\"thlex-xref\" data-bnType=\"lexiconLink\" data-collection=\"\" data-key=\"\" href=\"#\">3.9 蓄水池(cistern)&lt;REALIA:3.9&gt;</a> ）。在出現這三個詞語的其他經文中，並不確知這些洞或坑是天然形成的還是人造的。</p>\n</div>\n</div>",
